'''''Star Wars: X-Wing Tour of Duty: Imperial Pursuit''''' was the first expansion pack for the [[Star Wars: X-Wing (video game)|''Star Wars: X-Wing'']] video game, providing new missions for players. It was released in [[1993]] and was followed by the [[Star Wars: X-Wing Tour of Duty: B-Wing|''B-Wing'']] expansion later that year. Subsequent releases of the original game included both expansion packs. Once installed, the ''Imperial Pursuit'' missions appeared as "Tour of Duty IV" in the game.

==Opening crawl==
{{OpeningCrawl
|name=Tour of Duty IV<br />IMPERIAL PURSUIT
|text=Having achieved its greatest
